              "namespace": "harbor",
              "notes": "Please wait for several minutes for Harbor deployment to complete.\nThen you should be able to visit the Harbor portal at http://harbor.local:30002\nFor more details, please visit https://github.com/goharbor/harbor\n",
              "revision": 1,
